          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>School Overcrowding Reduction Act</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Education (ED) to award competitive grants to qualifying local educational agencies for activities relating to the construction of a school facility.</p> <p>In selecting grantees, ED shall prioritize agencies&nbsp;that demonstrate that grant amounts will be used to construct a school facility&nbsp;located within two miles&nbsp;of a school in which the&nbsp;average class size (excluding special education classes) exceeds 25 students. </p>]]></text>
        </item>
